name: Outdoor Gallery Series Presents: Sky + NFTartwolf
description:
NFTartwolf, the creator of H=N HOMIES, has been an early supporter of my work in the NFT space and I also adore her work! I love this project and wanted to exhibit and remix her Homie and mine, in a world where we could vibe out eternally. Also, you are welcome to vibe with us!

Homies created by NFTartwolf
Remixed by Sky Goodman

Video sculpted, animated, and edited by Sky Goodman

Music by modal_plane 

59 seconds
